file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: tshirt api for ecomm
  description: our first social app -swati
  version: 1.0.1
  contact:
  email: swatistiwati13@gmail.com
  url: "https://LCO.dev"


servers:
  - url: "{protocol}://localhost:4000/api/{version}"
    description: for local host
    variables:
      version:
        enum:
          - v1
          - v2
        default: v1
        protocol:
        enum:
          - http
          - https
        default: http


components:
  securitySchemes:
    cookieAuth:
     type: apikey
     in: cookie
     name: token
  BearerAuth:
   type: http
   scheme: bearer
